verbose_text: This indicates that in both cases PVP is completely removed from the gold nanoparticles, whereas the difference in the PVP content in Au/TiO 2 _ BHx5 and Au/TiO 2 _ BH, H 2 O is a result of the difference in the amount of TiO 2 -bound PVP, which has no effect on the Au LSPR band position and intensity.
